{"tid":956121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高級助理警務處處長李志恒日本小樽遇車禍　無生命危險","createTime":"2018-12-26T04:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T06:05:55.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7a054a8b4ba6e1069e22766e1e8efd5519d1c8af","tid":956121,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"高級助理警務處處長李志恒在日本小樽旅行期間遇車禍，他與同行6人被送往3間不同醫院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事發後，李志恒清醒但下身痳痺，無生命危險，透過入境處1868熱線轉介協助，由直升機轉往另一醫院。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨日，當時有兩輛車迎頭相撞，李志恒頸部受傷，已接受手術，同車其餘人士輕傷。警隊福利部及入境處派員到當地協助，李志恒自行致電回港向上司講述事件。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435059-20181226.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435059-20181226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nlZSAbnHmEPvOkfLRhKZ1MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=14401971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435059-20181226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aa13882a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435059-20181226.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f07da94b22a3bef4bc81e54444994cf179ba778f","tid":956121,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:33:33.000Z","msg":"呀sir炒車唔洗你教"},{"pid":"15e323c84706051877321a3fda2b7d39585b6f2f","tid":956121,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"比人告左不小心駕駛未"},{"pid":"7ef4217902e914cffe4cd5e8412a4e4576661053","tid":956121,"uid":44358,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:53:45.000Z","msg":"負皮係冇生命危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90626fab76fb5dc01050e3cd25d699f3eff1184","tid":956121,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"聽聞半身不遂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bcab57365effd